      "name": "Non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw ASTM F1717 applicability domain",
      "description": "Applicable to non-cannulated pedicle screw constructs with nominal diameter 7.0–8.0 mm, titanium alloy (Ti-6Al-4V), tested per ASTM F1717 static compression-bending protocol. Excludes cannulated designs, polyaxial-head variants, and dynamic fatigue loading regimes. Both laboratories must use calibrated load frames with traceable NIST calibration within 12 months of test date."
    },
