        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "Test samples acceptance criteria",
        "description": "N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested across two independent laboratories (Lab A: n=6, Lab B: n=5). All screws from same production lot; traceability to lot number documented. Inter-laboratory variability assessed; CV < 5% across labs for all QoIs. Achieves Gradation 3: replicate testing across independent laboratories with documented traceability."
      },
      "rationale": "Eleven constructs were tested across two independent laboratories using screws from the same production lot (Lot #NCT-2024-07). Lab A contributed 6 specimens and Lab B contributed 5 specimens. Inter-laboratory coefficient of variation was 2.8% (stiffness), 3.4% (yield force), and 4.1% (force at 40 mm), all below the 5% threshold. Full traceability from lot number to individual specimen test records is documented."
