        "description": "Validation activities use the same screw design, material lot, and test protocol as the intended COU. Testing performed at two independent laboratories with NIST-traceable equipment. Validation domain fully overlaps with COU operating envelope. Achieves Gradation 3: validation activities directly representative of the COU with multi-laboratory confirmation."
      },
      "rationale": "The validation activities used the identical non-cannulated 7.5 mm screw design, the same Ti-6Al-4V material lot, and the same ASTM F1717 protocol as the intended COU. Testing at two independent laboratories with calibrated equipment confirms reproducibility. The validation domain (load range, geometry, material) fully overlaps with the COU operating envelope defined in hasContextOfUse.hasOperatingEnvelope. This directly representative validation satisfies Gradation 3."
